    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, glass-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced strictly on schedule. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
